{"article_id":"nKOD7aT0UHc1PRw8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Taliban prisoner Sgt . Bowe Bergdahl pleaded guilty to charges of desertion and misbehavior before the enemy after a short military hearing at Fort Bragg , North Carolina , on Monday","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"after expressing doubts","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"that he could get a fair trial","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"after campaign statements by Donald Trump .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Interested in Bowe Bergdahl ?","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"Add Bowe Bergdahl as an interest","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Bowe Bergdahl news , video , and analysis from .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Add Interest","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"Despite surviving five years in a Taliban cage ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Bergdahl ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Trump said in several campaign speeches as a presidential candidate ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"was a `` traitor ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who should be executed .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"In an on-camera interview","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"shot last year by a British filmmaker ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"obtained exclusively by and airing today on `` Good Morning America , '' `` World News Tonight With David Muir '' and `` Nightline , '' Bergdahl says","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"the words of the man","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"who is now his commander in chief","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"would have made a fair trial impossible .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` We may as well go back to kangaroo courts and lynch mobs","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that got what they wanted , ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Bergdahl says .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` The people","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who want to hang me","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"- you 're never going to convince those people . ''","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Bergdahl , a 501st Parachute Infantry Regiment trooper , walked off his combat outpost in Afghanistan in June 2009","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"and was quickly captured by the Taliban .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"During his five years in captivity with the Haqqani Network","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- the same Taliban faction","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that held American Caitlan Coleman and her family hostage for five years","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"until they were freed last Wednesday -","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"he endured what one U.S. official called the worst case of prisoner abuse since the Vietnam War .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He was released in 2014 in exchange for five Taliban prisoners at Guantanamo Bay","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"- a deal","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that was harshly criticized on the campaign trail by then-candidate Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"who called Bergdahl `` garbage ''","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"and even suggested","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"that he should have been summarily executed .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"in the old days -","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"bing , bong , ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"as he mimicked firing a rifle .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` When we were strong . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Speaking to British war filmmaker Sean Langan ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"who was held captive by the same Taliban group in 2008 ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Bergdahl says","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"he wants to fight back against what he calls a false narrative","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"fueled by conservative outlets like Fox News","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that sought to portray him as a traitor and jihadi sympathizer","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"who had been persuaded to fight against the United States alongside his captors .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"it 's just insulting , frankly , ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Bergdahl tells Langan .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` It 's very insulting , the idea","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that they would think","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"I did that . ''","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"In 2014 , then-Fox News correspondents Megyn Kelly and James Rosen reported on `` secret documents ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"obtained by the network","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that purported to show","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Bergdahl had `` shown affection '' for his captors ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"converted to Islam","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and become a `` mujahid , '' or jihadi .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"According to Bergdahl , however ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"he thought","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"the conditions in captivity might kill him","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"before his captors could .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"`` It was getting so bad","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that I was literally looking at myself ,","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"you know ,","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"looking at joints ,","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"looking my ribs","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"and just going ,","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"' I 'm going to die here from sickness ,","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"or I can die escaping , ' ''","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"he says .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` You know ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"it did n't really matter . ''","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"He attempted to escape twice ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"according to military officials ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"and he was severely punished","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"after being recaptured .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Terrence Russell , a military official","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"who debriefs former U.S. captives for the U.S. Joint Personnel Recovery Agency ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"says","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Bergdahl was tortured in a way reminiscent of the brutality","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"visited upon prisoners of war in Vietnam decades ago .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"`` When they recaptured him","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and brought him back ,","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"the next day they spread-eagled","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"and secured him to a metal bed frame , ''","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"Russell says to Langan in another video .","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"`` They took a plastic pipe ...","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"and they started beating his feet and his legs repeatedly with this plastic pipe ...","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"The idea was to just beat him","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"and injure his legs and his feet","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"so that he could not walk away again . ''","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"Bergdahl also says","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"he was confined for more than four years to a cage","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"that was only 7 feet by 6 feet .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"`` From first year , ''","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"Bergdahl says","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"when asked how much time he spent in that cage .","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"`` So second , third , fourth and then into the fifth year . ''","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"It remains a mystery , however , why he walked off his post .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Another senior official","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"who spoke to Langan for his documentary","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"was retired Army Lt. Gen. Michael Flynn ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"who , as the former head of intelligence for special operations in Afghanistan and then as the director of the Defense Intelligence Agency , was deeply involved in the early search for Bergdahl .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"He also briefly served as Trump 's national security adviser","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"after working on his campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"and he tells Langan","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that he `` absolutely '' believes","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"Bergdahl left his base with the intention","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to meet the Taliban .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"But Bergdahl disputes that ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"saying in a taped conversation with filmmaker Mark Boal","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that was broadcast in the second season of the `` Serial '' podcast","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"that he walked off post in an attempt","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"to report to senior officers","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that his platoon commander was `` unfit '' for his position .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Bergdahl has not been charged with any crime","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"related to aiding the enemy .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Whatever his reasons were ,","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"at least two soldiers were seriously wounded during the search","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"to find him ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"as first reported in 2014 .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"In response to questions from Army Judge Col. Jeffery Nance on Monday , Bergdahl admitted multiple times","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"that he did not fully appreciate the enormity of his actions .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"`` At the time , I had no thoughts","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"anyone would come searching for me ...","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"however","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"looking back","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"I see","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"it was a very obvious mistake , \"","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"Bergdahl said .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"\" I believed","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"they would notice me missing ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"but I did n't think","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"they would pull off a crucial mission","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"to look for one private . ''","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"After his guilty plea , the question","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"remaining before the military","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"is what form of punishment Bergdahl deserves .","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"On that question , even Flynn doubts","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"that justice would be best served","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"by putting a former prisoner back in prison .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"`` So the guy deserted his men , his soldiers , his squad","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"- no doubt , ''","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"Flynn says .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"`` [ But ] I do n't think","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"he should serve another day in any sort of confinement or jail or anything like that ,","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"because frankly ,","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"even though he put himself into this situation to a degree ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"we","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"- the United States government and the United States military -","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"put him in Afghanistan . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":313,"left":160,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":0,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":163,"right":311,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":163,"left":162,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":4,"right":161,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":161,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":198,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":179,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":167,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":8,"right":166,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":166,"left":164,"right":165,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity